HEADWORD: Serried
<hw>Ser"ried</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Serry</er>.]</ety> <def>Crowded; compact; dense; pressed
together.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nor seemed it to relax their <qex>serried</qex> files.</q>
